 Mount a WIM File

dism /Mount-Wim /WimFile:"C:\path\install.wim" /Index:1 /MountDir:"C:\mount"


Explanation: Mounts the specified WIM file index to a local directory.

Unmount a WIM File
dism /Unmount-Wim /MountDir:"C:\mount" /Commit

Explanation: Unmounts the WIM file and applies any pending changes.

